@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ktesnj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.94 + v2 + 0.32) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.63)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.69) - (v2 + 0.11 / v0 + 0.44)) * wp.cos(v0))
    v0 = 0.00
    v0 = ((v0 * wp.abs(v1 + 0.59)) + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
